://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Pet-Shop-Boys-FKA-Twigs-Jorja-Smith-and-Father-John-Misty.-Credit-Jeff-Kravitz-Theo-Wargo-Samir-Hussein-and-Andrew-Benge-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Pet-Shop-Boys">宠物店男孩</a>， <a href="/artists/FKA-Twigs">FKA树枝</a>，<a href="/artists/Jorja-Smith">乔哈·史密斯（Jorja Smith）</a> ，<a href="/artists/Father-John-Misty">父亲约翰·米斯蒂（John Misty）</a>等人被宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/meo-kalorama">Meo Kalorama</a> 2025年的表演者。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/eight-reasons-to-head-to-meo-kalorama-festival-this-summer-3292983">今年夏天前往Meo Kalorama音乐节的八个理由</a></strong></li></ul><p>即将到来的节日版将在整个夏季看到该活动重返里斯本，并将在通常的Parque Da Bela Vista举行。一个新的变化是，该节日现在将在6月19日，20日至21日之间举行，而不是通常的夏季末期。 Meo现在将开始节日季节。</p><p> Keeping with the ethos of its commitment to diversity and inclusion within the musical curation, this year&#39;s line-up will also see the likes of <a href="/artists/Damiano-David">Damiano David</a> , <a href="/artists/Azealia-Banks">Azealia Banks</a> , <a href="/artists/The-Flaming-Lips">The Flaming Lips</a> <i>–</i> who will perform &#39;Yoshimi Battles The Pink Robots&#39;, L&#39;Impératrice, <a href="/artists/Róisín-Murphy">Róisín Murphy</a> , <a href="/artists/Scissor-Sisters">Scissor Sisters</a> , <a href="/artists/BADBADNOTGOOD">BADBADNOTGOOD</a> , <a href="/artists/Boy-Harsher">Boy Harsher</a> , BRANKO, Best Youth, Cara de Espelho， <a href="/artists/jasmine-4-t">Jasmine.4.T</a> ，<a href="/artists/Model-actriz">凯利</a><a href="/artists/Kelly-Lee-Owens">·李·欧文斯</a>（Kelly Lee Owens），马奎纳（Maquina。</p><p>现在可以<a href="https://meokalorama.pt/en/tickets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买节日通行证。 3天通行证可获得105欧元（88英镑，113美元）和一个朋友包（包括6张票，价格为5票），价格为525欧元（439英镑，566美元）。还提供付款分期付款计划。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGQCjzNAVVE/?utm