ef="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="米歇尔·麦克马纳斯（Michelle McManus）和罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）。图片来源：Tristan的少数和Dan通过Getty击中" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Michelle-McManus-and-Robbie-Williams.-Credit-Tristan-Fewings-and-Dan-Peled-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Robbie-Williams">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）</a>要求<em>流行偶像</em>冠军米歇尔·麦克马纳斯（Michelle McManus）在即将到来的巡回演出的一场比赛中与他一起表演二重奏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/robbie-williams-director-michael-gracey-biopic-better-man-interview-3821636">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）和导演迈克尔·格雷西（Michael Gracey）的香蕉，CGI猴子，以传记片“更好的男人”为特色：“它正在治愈”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-2025-uk-ireland-europe-tour-buy-tickets-3811519">从今年夏天开始，“ Rock DJ”命运者将在5月31日在爱丁堡举行的第一次跑步日期开始在英国，爱尔兰和欧洲进行大规模巡回</a>演出。</p><p>威廉姆斯（Williams）在麦克马纳斯（McManus）的下午表演中出现在<em>麦克马纳斯</em>（McManus）的下午演出时，威廉姆斯（Williams）在邀请她在他的一系列现场约会的第一站中与他一起表演，这使苏格兰<em>流行偶像</em>赢家感到惊讶。</p><p>威廉姆斯问道：“你想和我一起唱歌吗？”麦克马努斯回答：“对不起，对不起？那是什么？”。然后，“天使”的歌手重复了这个问题，麦克马努斯回答：“这是个玩笑吗？出于天哪，是的！”威廉姆斯随后回答了前唱歌节目冠军（2003年她赢得了<em>流行偶像</em>）：“让我们做。我们稍后会整理出什么歌。”</p><p>麦克马纳斯（McManus）出现在苏格兰<em>广播</em>电台的Drivetime计划中，并开放了有关威廉姆斯（Williams）的邀请，并告诉东道主，她确定歌手会在爱丁堡向她提出食物建议。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG3nhtIKj57/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.11