ay Night Live</a> &#39;s SNL50 afterparty. In turn, singer and actor <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/djo">Djo</a> – real name Joe Keery – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-djo-stranger-things-star-joe-keery-cover-haims-gasoline-3840070">covered Haim&#39;s &#39;Gasoline&#39; for Triple J&#39;s &#39;Like A Version&#39; series</a> a few days later.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-announce-friday-night-party-for-fans-in-london-following-comeback-single-announcement-3844278">Haim announce Friday night “party” for fans in London following comeback single announcement</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
